# YBM "face" format - monochrome bitmap by Bennet Yee (CMU, ~1988)
# Used by Yee's `face` and `xbm` programs for small Unix user portraits.
# Converters: netpbm (ybmtopbm/pbmtoybm), FBM library.

0	beshort	0x2121	YBM face image data,
>2	beshort	>0
>>2	beshort	<2049	%d x
>4	beshort	>0
>>4	beshort	<2049	%d
